<L>__{exterior street day}
<B>__{on a bus}
<A>__{as it pulls to a stop, the doors open and, along with the usual flood of mothers and children we see ted and billy. the camera tracks with them as they walk to school. billy is talking a mile a minute, describing in minute detail the plot of an episode of "i dream of jeannie." ted listens intently, then, almost involuntarily, he glances over his shoulder in the direction of the coffee shop.}
<B>__{his pov}
